{"ID":"20220706183228-2qvnk2y","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20220706183228-2qvnk2y","title":"王阳明心学（王德峰）","type":"doc","updated":"20220706184456"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220706184400-4limtgm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20220706184400-4limtgm","updated":"20220706184422"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"儒家的出世入世："}]},{"ID":"20220706183228-1d7izi7","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220706183228-1d7izi7","updated":"20220706184400"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20220706183259-4peyjy6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220706183259-4peyjy6","updated":"20220706183311"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"无所为而为："}]},{"ID":"20220706183311-aozqxnq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220706183311-aozqxnq","updated":"20220706184256"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t做一件事不是有目的的，不是为了做一件事而达到另一个有利于我们的结果，做种种的事情都因为这种种的事情本应当做，之所以努力的做这件事情因为这件事本身就是他的价值，他自己就是自己的价值。甚至可以凭借自己的经验和知识知道这件事做了以后的后果对自己是不利的，但我仍然去做，这叫知其不可为而为之！比如某个地区缺医少药，而我发现了这一点，创办了一家医院，但由于我不懂经济学不懂管理学等导致半年医院就破产了，那是代表我失败了吗？不，并没有，在这半年里我至少做了一件事——救死扶伤，并且这件事真的提醒了别人，这里真的该有家医院，于是让有本事的来吧，他呢叫当仁不让的来了，而我呢叫当仁而让，我没有失败。"}]}]},{"ID":"20220706183255-iwv2t0l","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20220706183255-iwv2t0l","updated":"20220706184444"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道家的出世入世："}]},{"ID":"20220706184445-tkwkhtl","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220706184445-tkwkhtl","updated":"20220706184454"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20220706184447-rjfwzr3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220706184447-rjfwzr3","updated":"20220706184454"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"无为而无不为："}]},{"ID":"20220706184454-gd4vhf0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220706184454-gd4vhf0"}}]},{"ID":"20220706184456-9utwv9g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220706184456-9utwv9g"}}]}